{"tid":2267931,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【專訪】辭職擲身家搞社區報 前《蘋果》記者何映彤給大埔人的一場實驗","createTime":"2020-11-02T12:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T05:55:35.000Z","uid":48083,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ac78632aac0f9b483be9cc5fa8a35c0e513156","tid":2267931,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ji4RLpH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJi4RLpH.jpg&h=f6f6dd39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒報導）對前《蘋果日報》記者何映彤（Vicky）而言，《埔JOURN》不單是一份社區報，或一本雜誌，也是她30年人生中最大膽的一場實驗。辭去做了6年的全職、擲全副身家自資出版社區報，Vicky說當社會充斥無力感，她想找一條新的道路，為社區帶來衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n拒絕資助眾籌、堅信紙本有價、用文字推動社區參與，是整個「實驗」的初衷。Vicky說自己其實「好驚」，甚至已預計了失敗的後路：「最多咪做返（傳媒）呢行，哈哈！」但無論結果如何，她也絕不後悔：「六期之後，如果我輸曬全部，都係冇所謂嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078570&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=e72d4b69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078570&h=3f112ae3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078570</a><br />\n<br />\n竹"},{"pid":"4c8449e899c9ed14ea64eeb17fc3433ee992ae05","tid":2267931,"uid":298578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a8aa81d961941796111f25ca1fdf0f24698088","tid":2267931,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922463c5381f1e